#: data/scripts/player/background/simulation/scoutcommandnotetable.lua:
msgid "We saw a very large, very old gate in this sector."
msgstr "Vimos una puerta muy grande y antigua en este sector."

#: data/scripts/player/background/simulation/scoutcommandnotetable.lua:
msgid "There is a big gate here."
msgstr "Aquí hay una gran puerta."

#: data/scripts/player/background/simulation/scoutcommandnotetable.lua:
msgid "A large, unusual, inactive gate is in this sector."
msgstr "En este sector hay una puerta grande, inusual e inactiva."

#: data/scripts/player/background/simulation/scoutcommandnotetable.lua:
msgid "Some strange, glowing asteroids in this sector. We stayed away."
msgstr "Algunos asteroides extraños y brillantes en este sector. Nos mantuvimos alejados."

#: data/scripts/player/background/simulation/scoutcommandnotetable.lua:
msgid "A very unusual ring of asteroids here. Are they charging something?"
msgstr "Un anillo de asteroides muy inusual aquí. ¿Están cargando algo?"

#: data/scripts/player/background/simulation/scoutcommandnotetable.lua:
msgid "An unnatural arrangement of asteroids with a weird signal in this sector."
msgstr "Una disposición antinatural de asteroides con una señal extraña en este sector."

#: data/scripts/player/background/simulation/scoutcommandnotetable.lua:
msgid "Some very odd people are gathered around a big asteroid here."
msgstr "Aquí hay unas personas muy raras reunidas alrededor de un gran asteroide."

#: data/scripts/player/background/simulation/scoutcommandnotetable.lua:
msgid "People around an asteroid. Lots of chanting."
msgstr "Gente alrededor de un asteroide. Muchos cánticos."

#: data/scripts/player/background/simulation/scoutcommandnotetable.lua:
msgid "I think there are people worshipping a rock in this sector. Really."
msgstr "Creo que hay gente adorando una roca en este sector. De verdad."

#: data/scripts/player/background/simulation/scoutcommandnotetable.lua:
msgid "It looked empty at first, but there's a wormhole here."
msgstr "Al principio parecía vacío, pero aquí hay un agujero de gusano."

#: data/scripts/player/background/simulation/scoutcommandnotetable.lua:
msgid "We almost stumbled straight into a wormhole in this sector."
msgstr "Casi nos tropezamos directamente con un agujero de gusano en este sector."

#: data/scripts/player/background/simulation/scoutcommandnotetable.lua:
msgid "Not sure where it goes, but there's a wormhole."
msgstr "No estoy seguro de adónde va, pero hay un agujero de gusano."

#: data/scripts/player/background/simulation/scoutcommandnotetable.lua:
msgid "An unusual satellite looping some research notes here."
msgstr "Un satélite inusual reproduciendo en bucle algunas notas de investigación aquí."

#: data/scripts/player/background/simulation/scoutcommandnotetable.lua:
msgid "A satellite in this sector talking about energy and stone."
msgstr "Un satélite en este sector hablando sobre energía y piedra."

#: data/scripts/player/background/simulation/scoutcommandnotetable.lua:
msgid "There's a satellite registered to 'M.A.D. Science' in this sector."
msgstr "Hay un satélite registrado a nombre de 'M.A.D. Science' en este sector."

#: data/scripts/player/background/simulation/scoutcommandnotetable.lua:
msgid "I couldn't believe it, but there are still people surviving in this sector."
msgstr "No lo podía creer, pero todavía hay personas sobreviviendo en este sector."

#: data/scripts/player/background/simulation/scoutcommandnotetable.lua:
msgid "Against all odds, there's a small outpost hiding from the Xsotan here."
msgstr "Contra todo pronóstico, aquí hay un pequeño puesto de avanzada escondido de los Xsotan."

#: data/scripts/player/background/simulation/scoutcommandnotetable.lua:
msgid "Some people claiming to be part of a resistance are stationed here."
msgstr "Algunas personas que afirman ser parte de una resistencia están apostadas aquí."

#: data/scripts/player/background/simulation/scoutcommandnotetable.lua:
msgid "A very strange ring of asteroids here. Xsotan energy signatures."
msgstr "Un anillo de asteroides muy extraño aquí. Firmas de energía Xsotan."

#: data/scripts/player/background/simulation/scoutcommandnotetable.lua:
msgid "There's a circular formation of strange, numbered asteroids here."
msgstr "Aquí hay una formación circular de extraños asteroides numerados."

#: data/scripts/player/background/simulation/scoutcommandnotetable.lua:
msgid "A ring of asteroids with inactive stations. Waiting for something."
msgstr "Un anillo de asteroides con estaciones inactivas. Esperando algo."

#: data/scripts/player/background/simulation/scoutcommandnotetable.lua:
msgid "An abandoned ship is here that looks largely intact. It may be repairable."
msgstr "Aquí hay una nave abandonada que parece en gran parte intacta. Puede ser reparable."

#: data/scripts/player/background/simulation/scoutcommandnotetable.lua:
msgid "A good repair crew might be able to get a ship we found flying again."
msgstr "Un buen equipo de reparación podría hacer volar de nuevo una nave que encontramos."

#: data/scripts/player/background/simulation/scoutcommandnotetable.lua:
msgid "A wreck in this sector is only lightly damaged. I bet we can repair it."
msgstr "Un pecio en este sector solo está levemente dañado. Apuesto a que podemos repararlo."

#: data/scripts/player/background/simulation/scoutcommandnotetable.lua:
msgid "Also, some sort of communication beacon was active here."
msgstr "Además, había algún tipo de baliza de comunicación activa aquí."

#: data/scripts/player/background/simulation/scoutcommandnotetable.lua:
msgid "We also detected a signal from some sort of beacon."
msgstr "También detectamos una señal de algún tipo de baliza."

#: data/scripts/player/background/simulation/scoutcommandnotetable.lua:
msgid "Oh, and there was a beacon broadcasting something about 'Exodus'."
msgstr "Ah, y había una baliza transmitiendo algo sobre 'Éxodo'."


# ==========data/scripts/player/background/simulation/simulation.lua ==========
#: data/scripts/player/background/simulation/simulation.lua:
msgid "Your captains continued working while you were away."
msgstr "Tus capitanes continuaron trabajando mientras no estabas."


# ==========data/scripts/player/background/simulation/simulationutility.lua ==========
#: data/scripts/player/background/simulation/simulationutility.lua:
msgid "I'll have regular data for you as the mission progresses."
msgstr "Tendré datos regulares para ti a medida que avance la misión."

#: data/scripts/player/background/simulation/simulationutility.lua:
msgid "You'll receive frequent updates as we learn more."
msgstr "Recibirás actualizaciones frecuentes a medida que aprendamos más."

#: data/scripts/player/background/simulation/simulationutility.lua:
msgid "Expect a continual flow of new information."
msgstr "Espera un flujo continuo de información nueva."

#: data/scripts/player/background/simulation/simulationutility.lua:
msgid "We have no deep scan ability and will have to visit every sector."
msgstr "No tenemos capacidad de escaneo profundo y tendremos que visitar cada sector."

#: data/scripts/player/background/simulation/simulationutility.lua:
msgid "Travel time will be extreme without more deep scan coverage."
msgstr "El tiempo de viaje será extremo sin una mayor cobertura de escaneo profundo."

#: data/scripts/player/background/simulation/simulationutility.lua:
msgid "We can't see where hidden mass sectors are without better radar."
msgstr "No podemos ver dónde están los sectores de masa oculta sin un radar mejor."

#: data/scripts/player/background/simulation/simulationutility.lua:
msgid "With our weak sensors, we'll waste a lot of time jumping blindly."
msgstr "Con nuestros sensores débiles, perderemos mucho tiempo saltando a ciegas."

#: data/scripts/player/background/simulation/simulationutility.lua:
msgid "We'd be a lot faster with more deep scan coverage."
msgstr "Seríamos mucho más rápidos con más cobertura de escaneo profundo."

#: data/scripts/player/background/simulation/simulationutility.lua:
msgid "Hidden mass sectors will be hard to find without better radar."
msgstr "Los sectores de masa oculta serán difíciles de encontrar sin un radar mejor."

#: data/scripts/player/background/simulation/simulationutility.lua:
msgid "There's a refinery right here, so this will be fast and safe."
msgstr "Hay una refinería justo aquí, así que esto será rápido y seguro."

#: data/scripts/player/background/simulation/simulationutility.lua:
msgid "Refining will be no problem with a depot right in this sector."
msgstr "Refinar no será un problema con un depósito justo en este sector."

#: data/scripts/player/background/simulation/simulationutility.lua:
msgid "I can autopilot right to the depot in this sector."
msgstr "Puedo volar con piloto automático directamente al depósito en este sector."

#: data/scripts/player/background/simulation/simulationutility.lua:
msgid "People are sure to appreciate our work here."
msgstr "La gente seguramente apreciará nuestro trabajo aquí."

#: data/scripts/player/background/simulation/simulationutility.lua:
msgid "This will help a lot of people."
msgstr "Esto ayudará a mucha gente."

#: data/scripts/player/background/simulation/simulationutility.lua:
msgid "Our generosity will help to build trust."
msgstr "Nuestra generosidad ayudará a generar confianza."

#: data/scripts/player/background/simulation/simulationutility.lua:
msgid "This isn't my specialty, but I'll see what I can do."
msgstr "Esta no es mi especialidad, pero veré qué puedo hacer."

#: data/scripts/player/background/simulation/simulationutility.lua:
msgid "A merchant would do this better, but I can give it a go."
msgstr "Un comerciante lo haría mejor, pero puedo intentarlo."

#: data/scripts/player/background/simulation/simulationutility.lua:
msgid "No merchants available, commander?"
msgstr "¿No hay comerciantes disponibles, comandante?"


